This is **planckUi**, a headless React Native UI library shipped as a **pnpm monorepo** with **Turborepo**. The codebase enforces token-driven styling, fixed component file layout, and strict lint rules. Before implementing a new component, read `.cursor/skills/build-component.md`. Before adding a named theme to the token pipeline, read `.cursor/skills/add-theme.md`. Before adding a hook under `packages/core`, read `.cursor/skills/add-hook.md`. Before authoring or updating Nextra docs, read `.cursor/skills/write-docs-page.md`.

Hard rules:
- Never hardcode hex, `rgb()`, `hsl()`, or named CSS colors in `packages/core` (use `get{Name}Tokens` + theme scales only).
- Never use Expo, NativeWind, or Tailwind in this library.
- Never use the `any` type.
- Never import another workspace package via relative paths (always `@my-ui-lib/tokens`, `@my-ui-lib/core`, etc.).
- Never hand-edit `packages/tokens/src/generated/`; regenerate via the tokens package build.
- Before reporting a task complete, run `pnpm typecheck` and `pnpm lint` from the repo root (or the relevant package) and fix failures.
- At the start of a scoped task, read the matching skill file end-to-end and follow it literally.
- When adding a new component, variant, or navigator pattern, integrate it into docs in the same task: add/update the docs page, menu entry, live preview, and install/setup guidance.
- If the docs page offers copyable implementation code, update the docs source explorer / generated source sync so the new files are copyable too; docs preview-only support is not enough.

Package names:
- Tokens: `@my-ui-lib/tokens`
- Core: `@my-ui-lib/core`
- CLI: `@my-ui-lib/cli`
- Docs app: `@planckui/docs`
- Example app: `apps/example`

Key paths:
- Component token helpers → `packages/tokens/src/component-tokens.ts`
- `SemanticTokens` → `packages/tokens/src/semantic.ts`
- Theme JSON overrides → `packages/tokens/src/tokens.input/themes/`
- Core components → `packages/core/src/components/`
- Core hooks → `packages/core/src/hooks/`
- Core public API → `packages/core/src/index.ts`
- Docs MDX → `docs/pages/`
- Docs live preview shell → `docs/components/Preview.tsx`
- Plop templates → `plop-templates/`
